    {
      "para_id": "p2",
      "section_id": "s1",
      "section_path": [
        "Usercentrics Response to the European Commission Call for Evidence – Digital Fairness Act"
      ],
      "ordinal": 2,
      "text": "Usercentrics, provider of both Usercentrics CMP and Cookiebot CMP, welcomes the European Commission's initiative to strengthen consumer protection and trust in the digital environment through the forthcoming Digital Fairness Act.",
      "char_len": 229,
      "chunk_word_count": 30,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.98,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8733624454148472
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.71,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p3",
      "section_id": "s1",
      "section_path": [
        "Usercentrics Response to the European Commission Call for Evidence – Digital Fairness Act"
      ],
      "ordinal": 3,
      "text": "As a leading European provider of Consent Management Platforms (CMP), we strongly support the Commission's efforts to address manipulative design patterns, deceptive interface practices, and other forms of digital unfairness that undermine user autonomy.",
      "char_len": 254,
      "chunk_word_count": 34,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9683257918552036,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8700787401574803
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.7623554550025138,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p4",
      "section_id": "s1",
      "section_path": [
        "Usercentrics Response to the European Commission Call for Evidence – Digital Fairness Act"
      ],
      "ordinal": 4,
      "text": "Digital fairness and privacy are deeply connected: both rely on transparency, informed choice, and user control. We therefore view this initiative as a vital opportunity to align consumer protection law and data-protection principles under a shared vision of fairness-by-design.",
      "char_len": 278,
      "chunk_word_count": 40,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9666666666666667,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8633093525179856
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.8527777777777779,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p5",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Privacy by Design as the Foundation of Digital Fairness"
      ],
      "ordinal": 5,
      "text": "The Digital Fairness Act should build on the EU's proven privacy-by-design approach to embed fairness directly into digital products and services. Designing for fairness means ensuring that consent, personalization, and commercial interactions are understandable, contextual, and free of manipulation.",
      "char_len": 301,
      "chunk_word_count": 40,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9657794676806084,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8737541528239202
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.8521123785382341,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p6",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Privacy by Design as the Foundation of Digital Fairness"
      ],
      "ordinal": 6,
      "text": "CMPs already operationalize these principles in millions of daily interactions—making data practices transparent, ensuring that consent is freely given, and providing auditable records of user choice.",
      "char_len": 200,
      "chunk_word_count": 27,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9771428571428571,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.875
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.6620238095238096,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p7",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Privacy by Design as the Foundation of Digital Fairness"
      ],
      "ordinal": 7,
      "text": "Rather than prescribing visual templates or fixed layouts, we encourage the Commission to adopt an outcome-based framework: regulate what fairness must achieve, not how it must look.",
      "char_len": 182,
      "chunk_word_count": 27,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.967948717948718,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8571428571428571
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.6551282051282051,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p8",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Privacy by Design as the Foundation of Digital Fairness"
      ],
      "ordinal": 8,
      "text": "Such an approach safeguards both creativity and legal certainty, allowing innovative UX solutions to flourish within a clear, enforceable set of principles.",
      "char_len": 156,
      "chunk_word_count": 22,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9777777777777777,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8653846153846154
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.586111111111111,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p9",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Privacy by Design as the Foundation of Digital Fairness"
      ],
      "ordinal": 9,
      "text": "Usercentrics is actively contributing to evidence-based policymaking through a government-funded research project focused on transparency and user understanding. The project explores how to make the concept of personalized advertising easier to explain to end",
      "char_len": 259,
      "chunk_word_count": 34,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9867256637168141,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8725868725868726
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.7761553588987218,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
