    {
      "para_id": "p40",
      "section_id": "s4",
      "section_path": [
        "Fairness Through Transparency and Interoperability"
      ],
      "ordinal": 40,
      "text": "Usercentrics therefore supports the creation of common standards for consent and fairness signaling—a shared \"language\" that enables different systems to communicate transparently without prescribing their internal logic or UI design.",
      "char_len": 234,
      "chunk_word_count": 31,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9804878048780488,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8760683760683761
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.7256436314363144,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p41",
      "section_id": "s4",
      "section_path": [
        "Fairness Through Transparency and Interoperability"
      ],
      "ordinal": 41,
      "text": "Such an approach reduces fragmentation, strengthens enforcement, and fosters innovation among European privacy-tech providers.",
      "char_len": 126,
      "chunk_word_count": 14,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9646017699115044,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8968253968253969
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.45400688298918385,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p42",
      "section_id": "s5",
      "section_path": [
        "Fairness Through Transparency and Interoperability",
        "Education and Empowerment Alongside Design"
      ],
      "ordinal": 42,
      "text": "We agree that education and awareness are essential complements to regulation. Citizens must understand their digital rights, but technology should also embody those rights through fair defaults and intuitive interaction models.",
      "char_len": 228,
      "chunk_word_count": 31,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9848484848484849,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.868421052631579
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.7289141414141415,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p43",
      "section_id": "s5",
      "section_path": [
        "Fairness Through Transparency and Interoperability",
        "Education and Empowerment Alongside Design"
      ],
      "ordinal": 43,
      "text": "Privacy-by-design and education are therefore mutually reinforcing: one embeds protection into systems, the other embeds it into society.",
      "char_len": 137,
      "chunk_word_count": 19,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9583333333333334,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8759124087591241
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.5256944444444445,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p44",
      "section_id": "s6",
      "section_path": [
        "Fairness Through Transparency and Interoperability",
        "Balancing Creativity and Consistency"
      ],
      "ordinal": 44,
      "text": "Usercentrics recognizes that Europe's strength lies in its diversity of ideas and interfaces. We share the view that over-standardization could lead to user fatigue and habituation.",
      "char_len": 181,
      "chunk_word_count": 26,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9743589743589743,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.861878453038674
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.6446581196581196,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p45",
      "section_id": "s6",
      "section_path": [
        "Fairness Through Transparency and Interoperability",
        "Balancing Creativity and Consistency"
      ],
      "ordinal": 45,
      "text": "However, consistency in principles, not uniformity in design, is what ensures fairness at scale.",
      "char_len": 96,
      "chunk_word_count": 14,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9518072289156626,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8645833333333334
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.4444109772423025,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p46",
      "section_id": "s6",
      "section_path": [
        "Fairness Through Transparency and Interoperability",
        "Balancing Creativity and Consistency"
      ],
      "ordinal": 46,
      "text": "The Commission should define clear criteria for manipulative or deceptive practices, while allowing businesses to implement compliant, user-friendly designs that fit their brand and audience.",
      "char_len": 191,
      "chunk_word_count": 25,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9760479041916168,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8743455497382199
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.6306470392548238,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p47",
      "section_id": "s7",
      "section_path": [
        "Fairness Through Transparency and Interoperability",
        "Toward a Fair, Transparent and Inclusive Digital Market"
      ],
      "ordinal": 47,
      "text": "A Digital Fairness Act grounded in privacy by design can strengthen Europe's leadership in ethical digital transformation. It can create a level playing field for responsible businesses while protecting vulnerable users and restoring trust in digital interactions.",
      "char_len": 264,
      "chunk_word_count": 37,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9868421052631579,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8636363636363636
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.8220760233918128,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p48",
      "section_id": "s7",
      "section_path": [
        "Fairness Through Transparency and Interoperability",
        "Toward a Fair, Transparent and Inclusive Digital Market"
      ],
      "ordinal": 48,
      "text": "Fairness and innovation are not opposing goals; they are interdependent.",
      "char_len": 72,
      "chunk_word_count": 10,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9682539682539683,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.875
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.4261904761904762,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p49",
      "section_id": "s7",
      "section_path": [
        "Fairness Through Transparency and Interoperability",
        "Toward a Fair, Transparent and Inclusive Digital Market"
      ],
      "ordinal": 49,
      "text": "By combining privacy-enhancing technologies, interoperable standards, and clear UX principles, Europe can ensure that every citizen's digital experience is transparent, respectful, and empowering.",
      "char_len": 196,
      "chunk_word_count": 23,
      "ratios": {
